lyrics:
[Verse]
Lost on this island, Christmas without cheer
No sign of rescue, feeling lonely and near
No gifts or loved ones, just solitude and fear
Waiting in darkness, as the end draws near

[Chorus]
Christmas on a lost island, feeling so blue
Hoping for salvation, but what can I do
No sleigh bells or laughter, just a heartfelt plea
Please rescue me from this deserted Christmas tree
